{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1328167, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz想得太简单了，维族同学来内地上大学都会被思想教育，爱疆教育一番。他们被禁止说有关的事情。不过就我身边的人来说，西域存在一些限制，但不存在灭绝。", "timestamp": 1616641724, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328174, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "？本新疆人根本不懂你在说什么？", "timestamp": 1616641767, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328177, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#政治相关#", "timestamp": 1616641796, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328182, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还西域？您老还真的大清遗老？", "timestamp": 1616641819, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328183, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 您怎么知道的？", "timestamp": 1616641821, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328187, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "md，维吾尔族生活的待遇比汉族好多，好吗？", "timestamp": 1616641862, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328189, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有新疆同学自己说的", "timestamp": 1616641883, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328192, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那我也是新疆同学", "timestamp": 1616641902, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328194, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我来和你讲讲？", "timestamp": 1616641920, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "去年内蒙古地区蒙语教学问题的时候，就有个疑似维族同学表示他自己当年差点进学习营，他自述他只是支持当地维语民族教学（即主课以维语授课+汉语学习），反对改为 主课以汉语授课+维语学习", "timestamp": 1616641939, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328198, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 有本事叫他或者她来和我对线", "timestamp": 1616641950, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328201, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 你当然可以讲呀", "timestamp": 1616641968, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328218, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "既然你已经默认了什么才是你想听的政治正确，我和你长篇大论有个什么用？新疆的分裂问题一直存在，打个比方就和香港废青的情况一样，不知您怎么看到这些事情呢？", "timestamp": 1616642144, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328219, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然我是觉得，如果你不会用维吾尔语和他们交流，可能是得不到他们的想法的（此发言含有民族偏执成分）", "timestamp": 1616642154, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328229, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我没有默认，我急需更多样本，所以真心请您讲解。不要吃枪药", "timestamp": 1616642212, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328236, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "觉得好像什么随随便便就进学习班？惶恐万分？本身就干着分裂民族投靠外国的事情，还吃着中国的饭，就不要怕鬼敲门！", "timestamp": 1616642244, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328241, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我没有get到，你到底在反感我啥，我说错了你可以纠正我，告诉我哪句话不对。我乐意接受批评", "timestamp": 1616642290, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328248, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "他们还不用汉语和我们说话呢？互相迁就迁就就可以了，你知道之前维语教育出了多么大问题吗", "timestamp": 1616642317, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328251, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 您是新疆少数民族还是汉族，还是兵团人", "timestamp": 1616642329, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328256, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "bob怎么了这是", "timestamp": 1616642389, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328257, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "维语历史课本里说他们的祖国是土耳其，画的都是新月旗", "timestamp": 1616642389, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328269, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "本身新疆的渗透都已经到根上了，大半个都快烂掉完了。", "timestamp": 1616642460, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328272, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 这个课本的事情我倒是听说过。", "timestamp": 1616642479, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328280, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "正常汉族人，但身边从下到大一直都有各族好朋友（维族、哈萨克、柯尔克孜、回族、蒙古满族、锡伯族）", "timestamp": 1616642543, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328282, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不是兵团人", "timestamp": 1616642554, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328287, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 看看看，来啊，政治正确啊？您可真可爱", "timestamp": 1616642585, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328289, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "课本这个事情最终被发现还是一个北京去当地的维吾尔学者去书店翻书发现的，由此可见自治区内部维汉隔离何其之深。遥想六十年代，汉族干部人均会说一定维语，不知道在17年前汉族干部会说维语比例有多少", "timestamp": 1616642606, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328294, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不懂就问，思想教育不是大学生都要受的吗？Alice是觉得马原毛概不算是思想教育？禁止说相关的事情自己就乖乖不说吗？说了会被行政拘留？", "timestamp": 1616642637, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328333, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "分裂从来都是从教育入手的，除了那个课本还有别的渗透，某些心怀不轨的维族人本身在各个系统里，就是在打着语言的旗号（我们听不懂汉语、只听维语）内部互相包庇。md，犯事了他们说我们听不懂汉语，要求维族警察审讯，但是审讯的结果就是没任何问题？开玩笑好吧？", "timestamp": 1616642866, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328345, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 没有这个意思啊，但是据同学说，要是说了会被请喝茶", "timestamp": 1616642959, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328356, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "统一回复,alice支持党和国家，没有任何怀疑论", "timestamp": 1616643079, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328366, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "另外，我们地区那里发生过人命事件，双方无冤无仇，但是那几个醉鬼就那么嚣张到直接杀人？最后事情也悄无声息地平了，但是汉族的人命不是命吗？别总在觉得维族是受欺压的，我可去你的。", "timestamp": 1616643196, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328387, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob:没有人觉得汉族人的命不是命吧，杀人凶手和极端组织当然要受到惩处，大部分怀疑的人只是希望能采取法制的手段", "timestamp": 1616643330, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328397, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "铁拳挥起来当然容易，但是国家要进步必须要靠法制的手段", "timestamp": 1616643405, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328407, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Bob大可不必过于激动，dy们也不是极端分子，只是想了解情况", "timestamp": 1616643470, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328441, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "本新疆人在这，怎么不来问啊", "timestamp": 1616643748, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328444, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "原来清华有这么多赵括2.0", "timestamp": 1616643775, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328449, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哦对连赵括都不如，起码人家还去了解了真实情况", "timestamp": 1616643798, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328528, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 讲讲？", "timestamp": 1616644372, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328669, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 懂王宁来🌶", "timestamp": 1616645954, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328736, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 💡大佐？", "timestamp": 1616646670, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328862, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 求懂哥细🔒", "timestamp": 1616647898, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1329732, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 之前那几个新疆同学的洞已经说的比较清楚了", "timestamp": 1616657126, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1329733, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 同上", "timestamp": 1616657137, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1333940, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "？我真的想不到还有人有这种疑惑？显然没有啊，在新疆生活了十几年出来一看别人对我们的印象是这样都惊了", "timestamp": 1616724797, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1336271, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 261186, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看来语言的壁垒一直没破除啊", "timestamp": 1616751691, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 13, "pid": 261186, "reply": 46, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "就没有维吾尔族同学说一下到底有没有剥削吗", "timestamp": 1616641570, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1616751691, "url": "", "vote": {}}}